{"title":"VGI","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Geriatría/VGI-2025-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"VGI","guid":"2PI1oI9JpfLn4MmNVY-qgQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Resumen ","guid":"UQv-g6sKb-NHHrB718Lizw","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"• Multidimensional y multidisciplinaria ➡ Evalúa capacidad funcional, salud física, cognición, salud mental, y circunstancias socioambientales.","guid":"90oQ9ZwdbhSlJsEk3eLMcA","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Componentes\\Nprincipales de la EGI","guid":"ikn687u1sNaoOnU1js_NkQ","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"1. Capacidad\\Nfuncional","guid":"c2YYnsfGl89obsHoUEfk3w","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"• Evalúa: Actividades de la vida diaria (AVD) ➡ básicas (vestirse, bañarse, comer)\\Ny instrumentales (usar teléfono, manejar finanzas).","guid":"xRz6hEBVxjLmQ6V76bfBug","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"• Herramientas: Índice de Katz, Escala de Lawton y Brody.","guid":"IvKWQxpVQ5j84iz0Fl2O3A","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"3","text":"2. Salud\\Nfísica","guid":"l4RjuhSbL5x1dXUtdlhn5g","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"• Evalúa: Nutrición, visión, audición, continencia fecal/urinaria, equilibrio.","guid":"vpKtE7AFjFpkINn9mPTYzQ","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"• Herramientas: Mini Nutritional Assessment, pruebas visuales y auditivas,\\NEscala de continencia de Wexner.","guid":"cyi-G9XCiXJGqXErZi2V_w","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"3","text":"3. Cognición","guid":"","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"• Evalúa: Función cognitiva y posibles demencias.","guid":"pHS58QyOOiLfQOILgOlMfw","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"• Herramientas: Mini-Mental State Examination (MMSE),\\NTest del reloj, Montreal Cognitive Assessment (MoCA).","guid":"zF6Ng9CS6Je9rMHv4yVWbQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"3","text":"4. Salud\\Nmental","guid":"8qeL9fjwTznyRou3mjKxFA","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"• Evalúa: Depresión, ansiedad, riesgo suicida.","guid":"OfXmQkbewmig5Gpi-zh8vg","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"• Herramientas: Escala de Depresión Geriátrica (GDS),\\NInventario de Ansiedad de Beck.","guid":"mo2WCkJz4zVy39X7HDtepg","children":[]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"3","text":"5. Aspectos\\Nsocioambientales","guid":"","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"• Evalúa: Soporte social, ambiente, riesgo de maltrato.","guid":"ifeETYrGl9ERBTPWS-Vetw","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"• Herramientas: Escala de Zarit, entrevistas sobre situación de vida.","guid":"RuMint6Fl_tKYcZbdoOhng","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"1","text":"Beneficios","guid":"y11KGxFeBKVaG_vMhthqHQ","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"• Dx más completo ➡ lista de problemas médicos, funcionales, psicosociales.","guid":"0eRWKTqlCDsELqKfeOyk1Q","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"19","text":"• Mejor desarrollo de plan de tto y seguimiento.","guid":"5V1KS9pa3l8E8Rap4M9bxA","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"19","text":"• Evaluación de necesidades de cuidados a largo plazo.","guid":"us4TIBhdR14Xp5RkjDNdMQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"1","text":"Implementación","guid":"n_qc-UOCl1K0-gb3kZkNmw","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"• Evaluación escalonada (“rolling assessment”) ➡ aborda problemas específicos en varias consultas.","guid":"hNbk5XkchttHHPDR-i8Oow","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"• Herramientas validadas permiten ahorro de tiempo y evaluación eficiente.","guid":"Pqyf1kZVnr2aBdEN3uoo4Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"1","text":"Recomendaciones\\Nclave","guid":"6m18XghL3PumAlaBD9yRnw","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"• Cribado para osteoporosis en mujeres ≥65 años (densitometría ósea) ➡ Evidencia A.","guid":"-kDtueeC2fF0lGhtx1suww","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"• Uso de audífonos en pacientes con pérdida auditiva ➡ Evidencia A.","guid":"uSALzUcfQRTTHBmjIKqs4A","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"• Uso de criterios de Beers en la evaluación de medicación para reducir efectos adversos ➡ Evidencia C.","guid":"o0Q0CZVZt9MpTGBS5GCVMA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"0","text":"Capacidad\\Nfuncional","guid":"_KdCNERVlZvPZPqydC82BQ","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"• Definición: Habilidad de realizar tareas necesarias para la vida diaria (AVD) e instrumental (AIVD).","guid":"Zc0xZJAVrhkdJhg9R7C7PA","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"• AVD (Actividades\\Nde la vida diaria)","guid":"4qy5FJVe7D7qPgUIGNBStg","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"• Autocuidado básico ➡ Comer, vestirse, bañarse, uso del WC, transferencias (cama/silla), continencia.","guid":"8I0Wa4Q45NmFwkOLJHwcVg","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"• Observación directa: tareas simples como desabotonar/abotonar, escribir, ponerse/quitarse los zapatos.","guid":"RTFfVWo9FdZBTvFMqUDf9w","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"1. Escala\\Nde Katz","guid":"3AWwRvQa1xYm_YTolgol1g","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"• Evalúa independencia en 6 actividades: baño, vestido, WC,\\Ntransferencias, continencia, alimentación.","guid":"NdcRMaec4205PVpTtGuYRg","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"35","text":"• Puntos totales (0-6) ➡ 0 = Dependiente total, 6 = Independiente.","guid":"xvspccXe4CQ2I6hUozH4PQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"30","text":"• AIVD (Actividades\\Ninstrumentales de la vida diaria)","guid":"sNcAEt2Ul7gz1ShRQhxlcQ","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"• Independencia ➡ Tareas como manejo de finanzas,\\Nmedicación, cocinar, realizar compras, uso de teléfono.","guid":"xwM9pOyoyY7od-8eDzDfqA","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"38","text":"• Deterioro en AVD/AIVD ➡ Indicativo de necesidad\\Nde evaluación socioambiental más profunda.","guid":"lJqAG6RgFtOMrAZuO0dW-g","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"38","text":"2. Escala\\Nde Lawton","guid":"YMk4yEotzWxv23ZjMGHHYQ","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"• Evalúa actividades instrumentales: uso de teléfono, transporte,\\Ncompras, preparación de comidas, manejo de finanzas, medicación.","guid":"m5kUzwtRij32JzmmsHhX6g","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"• Puntos (0-27) ➡ Declive en puntaje = Deterioro funcional.","guid":"EZAyV9pemquTgE_Oh8yCcA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"30","text":"Importancia","guid":"gFKk2YPccNuT9eA4PnlTdw","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"• Déficit en AVD/AIVD ➡ Necesidad de asistencia adicional y planificación de cuidados a largo plazo.","guid":"bHpIzbBv6pODDrkZCerEOA","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"• Evaluación periódica ➡ Detección temprana de declive funcional.","guid":"jlbZn3hI0r5H9la9HfD22g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"0","text":"Cribado de\\Nenfermedades","guid":"AdZRJ0klw5WmsAncwlqr5g","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"• Definición: Evaluación de personas asintomáticas para detección temprana de enfermedades.","guid":"Zq7zKEmKMJ3mLbaUI4rsdg","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"• Objetivos: Prevención de morbilidad futura ➡ Ej.: DM, HTA, glaucoma.","guid":"pdmUFtvf91JVkvu2FBatyw","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"47","text":"• Consideraciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"• Estado funcional, comorbilidades y esperanza de vida del paciente.","guid":"G75vAjTzqwwwXzmyMnBnZA","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"• Preferencias familiares respecto al tratamiento.","guid":"CDEU6cdZICspKO4yGh_eqA","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"50","text":"• Sobrevida >5 años ➡ cribado es médicamente justificado si el paciente aceptaría el tto precoz.","guid":"1NEEjGB0GtPamwNUt9Hbbg","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"47","text":"• Cáncer: Cribado importante para detección temprana y potencial curación.","guid":"uxq336FdJusyKB8C4ZCukg","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"47","text":"• Herramienta: Electronic Preventive Services Selector ➡ identifica medidas de cribado apropiadas para la edad.","guid":"BEmL71GJnjGKGZhCpMu-lw","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"47","text":"Examen físico\\Ngeriátrico enfocado","guid":"8AKbYFSbL_zGGOhEaW6a9w","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"1. Signos vitales","guid":"","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"• PA alta ➡ HTA, efectos adversos de medicamentos, disfunción autonómica.","guid":"xx2EBDKXp_XMW33ZexAvKA","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"• Hipotensión ortostática ➡ Medicamentos, aterosclerosis, cardiopatía isquémica.","guid":"ZL5fZQjOZ6nM9EkjspAohw","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"• Frecuencia cardíaca","guid":"cuzt2vARZNQx135OYmwRzw","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"• Bradicardia ➡ Medicación, bloqueo cardíaco.","guid":"UBXJH8_EmSTeVVPHaoYjFw","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"• Arritmia irregular ➡ Fibrilación auricular.","guid":"tpzatz31o-KSY7Yr5wNCTw","children":[]}]},{"id":"63","parent":"57","text":"• Frecuencia respiratoria >24/min ➡ EPOC, ICC, neumonía.","guid":"igz50usQgAJc-OWPKjcidA","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"57","text":"• Temperatura","guid":"MVNehz9_kmS88IyQVD45Ng","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"• Hiper/hipotermia ➡ Hipertiroidismo, hipotiroidismo, infección.","guid":"f9ojA1GsMXzkjQKIrcCYyQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"56","text":"2. General","guid":"","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"• Pérdida de peso no intencionada ➡ Cáncer, depresión.","guid":"fhCV_p2SC6iSriDGnX5flg","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"66","text":"• Aumento de peso ➡ Medicación (ICC).","guid":"SeOgVFIHGO94Nq--ILMY-w","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"56","text":"3. Cabeza","guid":"","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"• Debilidad/parálisis facial asimétrica ➡ Parálisis de Bell, ACV, AIT.","guid":"Bhvh7r5j4rK-SWDbi3Yp2g","children":[]}]},{"id":"71","parent":"56","text":"4. Ojos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"• Dolor ocular, visión afectada ➡ Glaucoma, DMAE, cataratas, arteritis temporal.","guid":"zNAcqO9EERnADTQWhfbAGg","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"71","text":"• Pérdida de visión central ➡ DMAE.","guid":"-gjMJBKFCUFKS_2ESGKFrA","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"71","text":"• Pérdida de visión periférica ➡ Glaucoma.","guid":"UyXWJ9-NtHqSGm-7cGNYAQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"56","text":"5. Oídos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"• Pérdida auditiva ➡ Neuroma acústico, cerumen, medicación ototóxica, audífonos mal ajustados.","guid":"y5pxm3XYySMbA59Pmxb7Sg","children":[]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"56","text":"6. Boca y garganta","guid":"","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"• Úlceras bucales ➡ Leucoplasia, síndrome de Sjögren, xerostomía.","guid":"cUtaYuJ1_PTduCFHI6G7OA","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"56","text":"7. Cuello","guid":"","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"• Soplos carotídeos ➡ Enfermedad cerebrovascular.","guid":"3quv-fYAf4tOz_2jD6HWHg","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"• Nódulos tiroideos ➡ Hipo/hipertiroidismo.","guid":"CGYzmuWuTTXe3epQHXRKgw","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"56","text":"8. Cardíaco","guid":"","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"• S4 ➡ Hipertrofia ventricular izquierda.","guid":"H_lfFCnbP8cRVM9a2fkb4A","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"• Soplos ➡ Estenosis aórtica, insuficiencia mitral.","guid":"gHev3bfLvonAXAvSX1YxDg","children":[]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"56","text":"9. Pulmonar","guid":"","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"• Tórax en tonel, disnea ➡ Enfisema, EPOC, ICC.","guid":"rjWgOtQszT-2uqfQT1JM9A","children":[]}]},{"id":"87","parent":"56","text":"10. Mamas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"• Masas ➡ Cáncer, fibroadenoma.","guid":"KeM9-J_BpC0SnbsIw3HtSw","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"56","text":"11. Abdomen","guid":"","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"• Masa pulsátil ➡ Aneurisma aórtico.","guid":"QOEoTHfz6coomdNU9wLHXg","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"56","text":"12. Gastrointestinal/Genitourinario","guid":"","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"• Atrofia mucosa vaginal ➡ Deficiencia de estrógenos.","guid":"NqZN8PwKKHFjwossSi3c5g","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"• Estreñimiento ➡ Cáncer colorrectal, hipotiroidismo, medicación.","guid":"L-3wunzuGF8eAMLPfSSLmQ","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"91","text":"• Nódulos prostáticos ➡ HBP, cáncer de próstata.","guid":"Uhs17bm4iop0BMzvZodcOQ","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"91","text":"• Incontinencia urinaria ➡ Prolapso vesical, inestabilidad del detrusor.","guid":"AI4mgLtUaIaLj8YGr2QZ0w","children":[]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"56","text":"13. Extremidades","guid":"","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"• Dolor y limitación de movimiento ➡ Artritis, fractura.","guid":"Hm3Ox31dVRpHaJQkJnPzmQ","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"• Dolor en pierna ➡ Claudicación intermitente, neuropatía, osteoartritis.","guid":"8axy6aX5WWakyUuCHDbtxQ","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"96","text":"• Edema pedal ➡ Insuficiencia venosa, ICC.","guid":"LKKb9-uNFwkjvCaRwWR1pQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"56","text":"14. Piel","guid":"","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"• Úlceras o eritema en puntos de presión ➡ Uso de anticoagulantes, maltrato, púrpura trombocitopénica idiopática.","guid":"Opw7IyesfzfcPPVIhEz-Qw","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"100","text":"• Lesiones premalignas/malignas ➡ Queratosis actínica, carcinoma basocelular, melanoma maligno, úlceras por presión.","guid":"cIihi2dee9dw2RTNGebNVQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"56","text":"15. Neurológico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"• Temblor con rigidez ➡ Enfermedad de Parkinson.","guid":"aJTw8eXSCCBwv1ZDMUws4w","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"0","text":"Nutrición en el adulto mayor","guid":"ybyIOmitdLCGd9iiJUFnHg","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"• Problema común: Deficiencias de micronutrientes (Vit A, C, D, B12; calcio, hierro, zinc).","guid":"JmTdFo4dLuHJkbtGibZtRQ","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"• Causas: Condiciones médicas relacionadas con la edad ➡ Ej.: anemia perniciosa, malabsorción.","guid":"dytaXpdkSNwkvm8o68kRMA","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"• Componentes de la\\Nevaluación nutricional:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"1. Historia nutricional ➡ Ej.: uso de un checklist de salud nutricional.","guid":"y8gKleH0uoLcG15STNzz9g","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"2. Registro de ingesta alimentaria ➡ Recordatorio de 24 horas.","guid":"aNckONB7KkaCdr8eRW0cgA","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"108","text":"3. Examen físico ➡ Signos de malnutrición o sobreconsumo.","guid":"Sl2sAyhoIz8kXFbqWvEKWQ","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"108","text":"4. Pruebas de laboratorio ➡ Solo si es necesario.","guid":"gfRBd69qs4wq5NqWGs73FQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"113","parent":"105","text":"• Herramienta: Nutritional Health Checklist.","guid":"EkNgaqBCOIr-jUdrzskY7w","children":[]}]},{"id":"114","parent":"0","text":"Visión","guid":"fYa_W63PxKvjWGTyHMfEuw","children":[{"id":"115","parent":"114","text":"• Causas comunes de deterioro\\Nvisual en adultos mayores:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"• Presbicia","guid":"BsbnZXtiSjG8hwg7TKUomA","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"115","text":"• Glaucoma","guid":"Ukdswh2TsKPJ0CW8qnMZww","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"115","text":"• Retinopatía diabética","guid":"2fR3tfvBC1sqvtq_XflfYg","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"115","text":"• Cataratas","guid":"N2tomXPHjH6MJQZJFPk4Vw","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"115","text":"• Degeneración macular asociada a la edad (DMAE)","guid":"DgQ9b5EzZfxvZUvx7Vd8tw","children":[]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"114","text":"• Cribado:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"• La USPSTF no recomienda ni descarta el\\Ncribado con oftalmoscopia en asintomáticos (15).","guid":"ax1L19mZc9BKkMwb3glfOQ","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"• La Canadian Task Force recomienda usar tabla de Snellen para evaluar agudeza\\Nvisual en AP y realizar examen oftalmológico en diabéticos con >5 años de evolución.","guid":"RqnKaSjkZCZzAfZfcywEHA","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"121","text":"• Pacientes en riesgo alto de glaucoma (diabetes, historia familiar, miopía grave, personas de raza negra)\\N➡ evaluación periódica por oftalmólogo (16).","guid":"bXX-z9xgNldQlFPzVFP24Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"114","text":"Herramientas de\\Ncribado visual:","guid":"PPM7BoZosekwC-R3bjAPuA","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"• Tabla de Snellen: Evalúa agudeza visual.","guid":"sEfyNevx2FkbNxl8MybaOw","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"• Evaluación oftalmológica: Para casos de diabetes o alto riesgo de glaucoma.","guid":"8qqbHgkRG0WOPAOqYatCWw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"128","parent":"0","text":"Audición","guid":"KluLq_T9ssrarXUN6BzjNA","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"• Presbiacusia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"• 3ra condición crónica más común en mayores\\N(después de HTA y artritis) (17).","guid":"LqqiphTz-gQrUI2iygKTfg","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"129","text":"• Pérdida auditiva relacionada con la edad\\N➡ afecta comunicación y calidad de vida.","guid":"bwndOnDbxekm_yzI5u-xAg","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"129","text":"• Cribado recomendado por la USPSTF","guid":"egNPbZiOIvA-a2UJyRUACg","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"129","text":"• Preguntar periódicamente sobre la audición.","guid":"-6eRFEMSZ0DyV54ojcxj3w","children":[]}]},{"id":"134","parent":"128","text":"• Uso de audioscopio, otoscopia y\\Nprueba de voz susurrada:","guid":"aYB5_7NLygvOl2aYlzdNFw","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"• Prueba de voz susurrada: Realizada a 3 ft del paciente, susurrando letras/números ➡ incapacidad de repetir la mayoría indica déficit auditivo (19).","guid":"e_P5cWuzLHAfavNMiP_ZEA","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"134","text":"• Cuestionarios de cribado ➡ Hearing Handicap Inventory for the Elderly (HHIE) (21).","guid":"LkNMZcX2qWTd3m95IgQM9A","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"134","text":"• Identifica impedimentos auditivos y grado de discapacidad (tabla 5).","guid":"ZCPT4SMDT1PjrDjWiUzucA","children":[]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"128","text":"• Medicación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"• Evaluar por uso de fármacos ototóxicos.","guid":"GhZgt9sMxSBfibIocyNrmA","children":[]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"128","text":"• Derivación a\\Nespecialista","guid":"39lPlJde4hhY_pk0vV2_XQ","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"• Otitis media crónica, pérdida auditiva súbita o falla en pruebas de cribado\\N➡ derivar a otorrinolaringólogo (21, 23).","guid":"mUVu5iWfy7NeqFnHsdbpZg","children":[]}]},{"id":"142","parent":"128","text":"• Tratamiento","guid":"","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"• Audífonos: 1ra opción para minimizar pérdida auditiva\\Ny mejorar la función diaria (23).","guid":"FuR06dMMTD3WJHBckFozqA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"0","text":"Incontinencia\\Nurinaria (IU)","guid":"MD3MhHbKkbogmi_JA_DVBg","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"• Definición: Fuga involuntaria de orina","guid":"YP-Rzt_7P0M_GoAWnXEMNw","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"144","text":"➡ afecta aprox. 15 millones en EE.UU,\\Nmayoritariamente personas mayores (24).","guid":"dR4CODFAwlQ0CbXYJoVTcg","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"144","text":"• Repercusiones\\Nmédicas:","guid":"_4Y2MAiEvVml2eA22fMkVg","children":[{"id":"148","parent":"147","text":"• Úlceras por presión.","guid":"NmN0N4ZGPujXpXaNOi4HGw","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"147","text":"• Sepsis.","guid":"5FNpOGPDq8QTgQlsAjia2Q","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"147","text":"• Insuficiencia renal.","guid":"tyQXo-QUH732WhrghicKiA","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"147","text":"• Infecciones urinarias recurrentes.","guid":"FQ_padtq0cI2jIk9WWUXwQ","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"147","text":"• Aumento de la mortalidad.","guid":"fqnCeKfVToyBEyC2VwZVVQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"153","parent":"144","text":"• Implicancias\\Npsicosociales:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"• Pérdida de autoestima.","guid":"Q2TGgXThMWvh17Mw1o7r2A","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"153","text":"• Restricción de actividades sociales y sexuales.","guid":"skHIZi_sLGkUGaue3MhLMg","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"153","text":"• Depresión.","guid":"uBUKAqtVaOl9WcqrhsFCpQ","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"153","text":"• Factor decisivo para institucionalización en hogares de ancianos (25).","guid":"qLxPwp_YmEd0Rx5UUdnhag","children":[]}]},{"id":"158","parent":"144","text":"Evaluación\\Nde IU","guid":"1JTUIpAtFcZ73j3rTyCJew","children":[{"id":"159","parent":"158","text":"• Aspectos\\Na evaluar:","guid":"EXzGRUit0sDj_TDU2wLCPw","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"• Ingesta de líquidos.","guid":"gWMPCO4asKZdoh3gy5DT7A","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"• Uso de medicación.","guid":"RqqeBzRGh5BJ-b_kGgO68w","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"159","text":"• Función cognitiva.","guid":"dMCdRVxmcPnTIWOQwsp2Ew","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"159","text":"• Movilidad.","guid":"wT1RB_u6VBX8IcAlfV3ckA","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"159","text":"• Cirugías urológicas previas.","guid":"xStmgsdzCIYB5hU3nuAuaQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"165","parent":"158","text":"Tipos de\\Nincontinencia","guid":"18ohRAhetqjA8FKUohxfSw","children":[{"id":"166","parent":"165","text":"1. Incontinencia\\Nde urgencia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"• Pregunta clave: “¿Tiene una necesidad urgente y repentina\\Nde orinar que hace que se escape antes de llegar al baño?”","guid":"moqDTb73HONVSne_Yv8TLA","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"166","text":"• Razón de probabilidad positiva: 4.2; negativa: 0.48 (26).","guid":"dN93Owj_IhE5x2oGzS4Vjg","children":[]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"165","text":"2. Incontinencia\\Nde esfuerzo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"• Pregunta clave: “¿Su incontinencia es causada por\\Ntoser, estornudar, levantar objetos, caminar o correr?”","guid":"yOeKRw5kDHE9zTZNdXa0MA","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"• Razón de probabilidad positiva: 2.2; negativa: 0.39 (26).","guid":"P8Df-MXLuFptUtEiUCdghg","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"172","parent":"0","text":"Balance y prevención\\Nde caídas","guid":"4dkpOm15cKYq_-EyBqwEew","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"• Prevalencia:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"• 1/3 de personas mayores en comunidad\\Ncaen al menos una vez al año (27, 28).","guid":"dG9jo3JshFMx2WSzR95Rbg","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"• Causa principal de hospitalización y\\Nmuerte por lesiones en >75 años (29).","guid":"5LAhBePzRZ0d7Dk962hPdg","children":[]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"172","text":"• Evaluación del\\Nriesgo de caídas","guid":"u1Paaf0newFpO0Y6ah7q8g","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"• Prueba de equilibrio y\\Nmarcha de Tinetti (28, 30):","guid":"1VAMze_pIMZMFxpt6cZK4w","children":[{"id":"178","parent":"177","text":"• Paciente se levanta de una silla sin usar brazos,\\Ncamina 10 ft, gira, vuelve y se sienta.","guid":"1iGfPJNTFT6lFUmI-Nx6Wg","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"177","text":"• Tiempo <16 seg ➡ dificultad = mayor riesgo de caída\\N➡ evaluación adicional necesaria (31).","guid":"v6Dl6tqnR_SD490iZ7141g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"180","parent":"172","text":"• Intervenciones para\\Nreducir riesgo de caídas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"• Ejercicio.","guid":"ZjwMuF57EDChZg9-BRdKpw","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"180","text":"• Terapia física.","guid":"nuHqWAY09UUTNqeteMR3yg","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"180","text":"• Evaluación de riesgos en el hogar.","guid":"4Aq2HgXuexHFsJU5TQDyhw","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"180","text":"• Retiro de medicamentos psicotrópicos.","guid":"dKQ01GiAcqDLxRELJ4RDpA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"185","parent":"0","text":"Osteoporosis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"• Riesgo de fracturas por fragilidad:","guid":"4CUsbwvj0on-4x8oHoukVA","children":[{"id":"187","parent":"186","text":"• Fracturas de bajo impacto o espontáneas pueden llevar a caídas (14).","guid":"ScC4cM1IHUEI1RtnJGxIig","children":[]}]},{"id":"188","parent":"185","text":"• Dx: Densitometría ósea (DXA) de cadera total, cuello femoral o columna lumbar.","guid":"7uR4Uw5YdUEjI02SfYwp-w","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"185","text":"• T-score ≤ -2.5 ➡ Osteoporosis (35, 36).","guid":"-iAIwvOZ-gTmbmiYghOD1g","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"185","text":"• Cribado recomendado en mujeres ≥65 años (37).","guid":"seLnWLdRoXSwcUoGtOy16Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"191","parent":"0","text":"Polifarmacia","guid":"SIypPAJ1Uy-jw1X-4WW-KQ","children":[{"id":"192","parent":"191","text":"• Definición: Uso de múltiples medicamentos o más de los clínicamente indicados.","guid":"VwxRAbPFAHrCAJNubyWUfw","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"191","text":"• Consecuencias:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"• 30% de hospitalizaciones en mayores.","guid":"3LyRhADBVjosPlccBFES1g","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"• Problemas prevenibles como caídas y confusión,\\Nrelacionados con efectos adversos (38).","guid":"_wbglBXG749pP9fbJCRrcQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"191","text":"• Criterios de Beers: Lista de medicamentos a evitar en mayores (39, 40).","guid":"UOUrG0DCyfP9rPpI_BK8QQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"197","parent":"0","text":"Depresión","guid":"yaLC0gt2Pv6hpI1lxK1oew","children":[{"id":"198","parent":"197","text":"• Recomendación USPSTF: Cribado en adultos\\Nsi existen sistemas de atención adecuados (42).","guid":"Qv03rR2pP5zBbnos2CgZUA","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"197","text":"• Instrumentos validados:","guid":"nypS0NFWNyDz1vEsjqrgKw","children":[{"id":"200","parent":"199","text":"• Escala de Depresión Geriátrica (GDS).","guid":"4pevjWhVHM2RP--TpjZiAA","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"199","text":"• Escala de Depresión de Hamilton.","guid":"orzQAmQZWMOdMDQ53eqwKQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"202","parent":"197","text":"• Herramienta simplificada\\N(43, 44):","guid":"7w-agRBZnaiSmBA7N6At0w","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"1. “¿En el último mes, se ha sentido triste, deprimido o sin esperanza?”","guid":"sXVEjRsn6dpyKRsnQlwrUA","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"202","text":"2. “¿Ha sentido falta de interés o placer en hacer cosas?”","guid":"mkB1NlmmliGXBp16hjUOFg","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"202","text":"• Responder afirmativamente a ≥1 pregunta\\N➡ Cribado positivo ➡ evaluación adicional.","guid":"60yg9mwgFXwTJ5sA6wrQmA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"206","parent":"0","text":"Demencia","guid":"QE3SZecCqnckqsvBchZAJw","children":[{"id":"207","parent":"206","text":"• Beneficios del\\Ndx temprano:","guid":"9uxTbx79GKgq9DTgD0d91Q","children":[{"id":"208","parent":"207","text":"• Acceso oportuno a medicación.","guid":"6LgxEkYxk2oXq2VtmOWACw","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"207","text":"• Preparación familiar para el futuro.","guid":"BL_3xC9f6SLoubf4PUXrbw","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"207","text":"• Manejo de síntomas asociados (depresión, irritabilidad).","guid":"mJcim_-dy7ZoP9QOM-kTqg","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"207","text":"• Solo 50% de casos de demencia son diagnosticados por médicos (45).","guid":"2blRFyw-9mgkEuht4rMsVw","children":[]}]},{"id":"212","parent":"206","text":"• Test preferido:","guid":"frf5LCrRmi25J-JdPjao6w","children":[{"id":"213","parent":"212","text":"• Mini-Cognitive Assessment Instrument ➡ rápido,\\Nconveniente, no requiere fluidez en inglés (46, 47).","guid":"Q